{
  "texts": [
    "Employing sentiment analysis, stance detection, and emotion recognition with fake news detection still needs more investigation, especially in relation to the responses of the crowd.",
    "Moreover, features related to networks are still not investigated in fake news in the Arabic language, except for the work performed by [75].",
    "Traditional machine learning approaches, such as SVM, LR, and KNN, are the most used in Arabic research.",
    "Based on the review, most research in Arabic has used language models, such as AraBERT, MARBERT, mBERT, and QARiB.",
    "Research using the ensemble techniques is scarce, and there is a need for more studies applying this model."
  ]
}